data.title: Sexy South Of The Border! Victoria's Secret Model Lais Ribeiro Takes A Dip In Mexico Wearing Skimpy Orange Bikini — Photos
data.meta_description: Victoria's Secret model Lais Ribeiro was spotted taking a dip in the ocean while on vacation in Tulum, Mexico, on Monday, March 29.
data.text:

Article continues below advertisement

Fun in the sun! Victoria's Secret model Lais Ribeiro was spotted taking a dip in the ocean while on vacation in Tulum, Mexico, on Monday, March 29.

The Brazilian beauty worked her famous figure in a skimpy orange two-piece bikini, featuring a tiny triangle top and matching side-tie, thong bottoms.

Article continues below advertisement

Article continues below advertisement

The 30-year-old, who is engaged to NBA star Joakim Noah, is currently living her best life south of the border with fellow VS model and BFF Candice Swanpoel.

Article continues below advertisement

Scroll through the gallery below to see more pics from the model's ocean outing.

Article continues below advertisement

Prior to becoming a model, Ribeiro was in training to become a nurse. After giving birth to her son Alexandre in 2008, she gave in to a friend's advice and started working as a model in her native Brazil.

Article continues below advertisement

Clearly a natural, by 2009, she was walking the major international catwalks for such designers as Chanel, Louis Vuitton, Gucci, Dolce & Gabbana, Versace, DKNY, Dior, Roberto Cavalli, Blumarine, Moschino, Balmain, Jean Paul Gaultier, Alexandre Vauthier, Elie Saab, Alexander Wang, Marc Jacobs and more.

Article continues below advertisement

Article continues below advertisement

She has also been photographed for American, Brazilian, German and Italian versions of Vogue and appeared in ad campaigns for Ralph Lauren, Christian Dior, Tom Ford, GAP and American Eagle.

Article continues below advertisement

In 2010, she made her Victoria's Secret Fashion Show debut and became an official Angel in 2015.
